WEBVTT

00:00:07.702 --> 00:00:09.102
Namaste.

00:00:09.502 --> 00:00:11.192
I'm from India.

00:00:11.192 --> 00:00:14.214
The home of ancient mathematics.

00:00:14.214 --> 00:00:17.423
But me, I just hated math.

00:00:17.423 --> 00:00:19.141
(Laughter)

00:00:20.041 --> 00:00:22.442
Until it saved my life.

00:00:24.492 --> 00:00:29.924
I grew up in Akola, a small town
700 miles away from the capital city.